title_english: Gude Crest: The Emblem of Gude
title_japanese: 女戦士エフェ&ジーラ グーデの紋章
title_synonyms: Female Soldiers Efe and Jeila: Crest of Gude
Onna Senshi Efe & Jira: Guude no Monshou
synopsis: Two partners Effera and Jiliora escape from a slave boat with the aid of their friend Orlin and a young boy named Kilian. When Kilian is killed in the escape Effera and Jiliora take it upon themselves to return Kilian's pendant to his two siblings who are being held captive by Baron Celdion, who is plotting to take over all of the neighboring countries. (Source: ANN)
ending_themes: "Start Up - Tobitatsu Hi" by Naoko Matsui and Kazue Ikura
